## About the project üí≠

For Project #2 at Ironhack Web Development Bootcamp, we came up with the idea of creating a personal Concert Database inspired by our passion for music and live concerts. The goal‚Äôs to keep track of the shows we have been to, with a few information such as Tour name, Artist, year and so on.

## Netlify Deploy üìù

You can find the app deploy [here!](https://concert-database.netlify.app/)
